        <num>47-24-101</num>
        <content>
          <p>Upon retirement under subsection (a) of Code Section 47-24-100, the retired member shall receive a monthly service retirement allowance of $50.00 plus an additional $5.00 per month for each year of creditable service over 20 years, up to a maximum monthly benefit of $100.00.</p>
